DISCOVER EAGLE HARBOR: A PEACEFUL RV & MANUFACTURED HOME COMMUNITY IN OKEECHOBEE, FL
Eagle Harbor is a cozy RV and manufactured home community located directly on the shores of Lake Okeechobee in Okeechobee, Florida. Known for its laid-back atmosphere and beautiful waterfront views, Eagle Harbor offers residents a peaceful place to call home—whether you’re staying seasonally or settling in for the long term. With a private boat dock on-site, it’s an ideal location for fishing, boating, or simply enjoying the tranquility of lakefront living.
What makes Eagle Harbor truly special is its connection to the nearby Zachary Taylor RV Resort, our sister property just minutes away. As a resident of Eagle Harbor, you have full access to all of Zachary Taylor’s resort-style amenities and community events. From the heated swimming pool and clubhouse to a full calendar of activities and gatherings, you’ll enjoy the vibrant social life and recreational perks of a larger resort—while coming home to the quiet comfort of Eagle Harbor.
